     FAKBPL03 IF  E           K        DISK
     FGDMPL10 IF  E           K        DISK
     FGDMWP20 O   E                    DISK
      ******************************************************
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
     I* SYSTEM DATE & TIME
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WWTIME
     I                                        1   60WTIME
     I                                        1   40WTIM4
     I                                        7  120WSDATE
     I                                        9  120@@YM4
     I                                        7  120@@YM6
     I                                        7  140@@YMD
     I                                        7  100@@YY
     I                                       11  120@@MM
     I                                       13  140@@DD
     I            DS
     I                                        1  14 W@SHIN
     I                                        1   5 W@SHN1
     I                                        6   6 W@SHNA
     I                                        7  11 W@SHN2
     I                                       12  12 W@SHNB
     I                                       13  14 W@SHN3
     I            DS
     I                                        1   9 W@TKRO
     I                                        1   1 L1TKR1
     I I            '-'                       2   2 W@TKRA
     I                                        3   4 L1TKR2
     I I            '-'                       5   5 W@TKRB
     I                                        6   7 L1TKR3
     I I            '-'                       8   8 W@TKRC
